LANG_ENGLISH        "^1REZNOV: ^7Ti hanno visto!"

REFERENCE           REBIRTH_VOX_REB1_S99_312A_REZN
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1REZNOV: ^7Non farti vedere!"

REFERENCE           REBIRTH_VOX_REB1_S99_313A_WEAV
LANG_ENGLISH        "^1WEAVER: ^7Hudson, dove stanno andando?"

REFERENCE           REBIRTH_VOX_REB1_S99_314A_WEAV
